2006-11-03 15:12  djcb

	* scripts, scripts/modest-parse-presets.pl, src/modest-presets.c,
	  src/modest-presets.h: * added scripts/modest-parse-presets.pl,
	  src/modest-presets.[ch]:
	  imported first iteration of the presets system, which will allow
	  modest
	  to use preset provider info (mailservers etc.). the system uses
	  an existing
	  excel-sheet with this information, and the perl script translates
	  this into
	  a GKeyFile understood by modest-presets.[ch]. This excelsheet has
	  not been
	  checked-in yet.

